caption.p: Dose-response curves of potent SARS-CoV-2 3CLpro inhibitors. The inhibitory activity of (A) Ethacrynic acid, (B) Naproxen, (C) Allopurinol, (D) Butenafine hydrochloride, (E) Raloxifene hydrochloride, (F) Tranylcypromine hydrochloride, and (G) Saquinavir mesylate against SARS-CoV-2 3CLpro are shown, along with a depiction of the chemical structure. Data ( N = 3) are expressed as the mean ± SEM.
